These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, oliveros, pall-mall, davidoff
1. the oliveros-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the davidoff-smoker is between the havana-smoker and the oliveros-smoker##2
3. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Cigar   | havana | davidoff | oliveros | pall-mall |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, german, american, malaysian
1. the pakistani is on the left of the malaysian##1
2. the german is in an odd position##4
3. the german is on the left or right of the pakistani##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Nationality   | german | pakistani | malaysian | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, social-worker, entrepreneur, engineer
1. the engineer is on the left or right of the musician##3
2. the musician is in an odd position##4
3. the entrepreneur is between the engineer and the social-worker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Job   | musician | engineer | entrepreneur | social-worker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, photography, sudoku, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Hobby   | photography | dancing | collecting | sudoku |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different games are played: whist, poker, go, monopoly
1. the person playing whist is in an even position##4
2. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing whist##1
3. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing go##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Game   | monopoly | whist | go | poker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, airplane, skateboard
1. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
3. the person driving the airplane is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Transport   | airplane | bike | skateboard | car |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, april, september, january
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
2. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in april##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Birthday   | january | august | september | april |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-8::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, superhero, zombie, family
1. the person watching superhero movies is in an even position##4
2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2       |     3      |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | superhero | family | drama |

