.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
House: farmhouse, victorian, gothic-revival, futuristic
1. the futuristic house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
2. the victorian house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
3. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
4. the futuristic house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| House   | gothic-revival | futuristic | farmhouse | victorian |

