.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, firefighter, coach, musician
1. the firefighter is the firefighter##1
2. the musician is on the left or right of the coach##3
3. the coach is on the far left or far right##3
4. the journalist is in an even position##4
5. the musician is on the left of the firefighter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Job   | coach | musician | firefighter | journalist |

