.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, drama, martial-arts, romance
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | romance | martial-arts | drama |

 